Package com.marsG.simplerandomorglib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RandomIntegerClient
    Simple Http client to facilitate getting random integers, in binary, hexadecimal, octal or decimal form, generated by 'random.org' website.(http://www.random.org) Please set userClient field to your e-mail address, so Dr.Haar can contact you in case this client misbehaves.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NotEnoughQuotaException
    NotEnoughQuotaException is thrown when the client's quota < 0.
